body.description: Unleash the power of high-speed data transfer with the Kingston 512GB DataTraveler Max USB 3.2 Gen 2 Type A Flash Drive (DTMAXA/512GB). This USB flash drive redefines portable storage with its impressive read speeds of up to 1000MB/s, providing swift access to your files, documents, and multimedia. It also boasts a write speed of 900 MB/s which allows for quick downloads of any file or media you may need. With a capacious 512GB storage capacity, the DataTraveler flash drive is your go-to solution for carrying large files and data on the go. The USB 3.2 Type A interface ensures universal compatibility with a wide range of devices, from computers to smart TVs and more. Its compact and durable design makes it the perfect companion for professionals, students, and anyone in need of reliable and high-performance storage. This drive had a design built to protect itself with a sliding protector you can take it on the go without fear of damaging the USB port or the files stored inside. Included in the bundle is the Everything But Stromboli Lanyard, adding a touch of convenience and style to your flash drive. This lanyard not only facilitates easy carrying but also complements the sleek design of the Kingston Flash Drive. Elevate your data transfer experience and stay organized with the Kingston 512GB DataTraveler Max USB Flash Drive bundle, combining blazing-fast speeds with a capacious storage solution. This Bundle comes with (1) 512GB Kingston DataTraveler Max Flash Drive and (1) Everything But Stromboli Lanyard.
